    "body": "Also, I could not reproduce the issue:\r\n\r\nRunning the following command using `Nethermind.Cli`:\r\n\r\n```\r\neth.estimateGas({from: \"0x9d055dd23de15114ec95921208c741873ede8558\", to: \"0xe74bc1c4c27284ab7dbcf55f71fcc04b832fc32c\", data: \"\"})\r\n```\r\n\r\n*Note: the JSON body is the same as in the gist*\r\n\r\nI get the following outputs based on the node address:\r\n- `https://rpc.gnosis.gateway.fm`: `\"0x58e8\"` (official Gnosis Chain RPCs)\r\n- `http://localhost:8545/`: `\"0x6518\"` (local Nethermind)\r\n\r\nNote that Nethermind produces a higher estimation, not lower.\r\n\r\nAll Nethermind tools (`CLI` and `Runner`) are using version 1.21.0-unstable (commit 43660b6a730730b9cd561f116cf546660fabe6da)\r\n",
